OL,3,CRicky Hatton's dad speaks for first
OL,4,Ctime about loss of his son
OL,6,FRay Hatton said his son's legacy will
OL,7,Fnever be forgotten
OL,9,FThe father of former world boxing
OL,10,Fchampion Ricky Hatton has spoken
OL,11,Fpublicly for the first time about the
OL,12,Floss of his son.
OL,14,FIn an exclusive chat with Granada
OL,15,FReports, Ray Hatton thanked the public
OL,16,Ffor their outpouring of love and
OL,17,Fsupport since Ricky's death in
OL,18,FSeptember 2025, but admitted their
OL,19,Fkindness has "made it even harder" for
OL,20,Fthe family.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
