FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778702756
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's dad speaks for first
OL,4,Ctime about loss of his son
OL,6,FRay visited his son's gym in Hyde on
OL,7,FWednesday 13 May, to watch one of
OL,8,FRicky's former opponents Paulie
OL,9,FMalignaggi, in a training session
OL,10,Fahead of a fight in Manchester this
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,13,FRay Hatton told Granada Reports sports
OL,14,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall that IT was
OL,15,F"overwhelming" to be in the gym for
OL,16,Fthe first time since Ricky's passing.
OL,18,FHe said: "People mean well, and we
OL,19,Fappreciate everything, but people
OL,20,Fbeing kind to us actually makes it
OL,21,Fharder sometimes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778702756
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's dad speaks for first
OL,4,Ctime about loss of his son
OL,6,F"But his legacy is there, he will
OL,7,Fnever be forgotten, and that's all we
OL,8,Fcan ever dream of."
OL,10,FRicky was found unresponsive at his
OL,11,Fhome in Hyde by his manager on 14
OL,12,FSeptember 2025.
OL,14,FAn inquest into his death in March
OL,15,Ffound it was not clear that he
OL,16,Fintended to take his own life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
