OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778702756
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's dad speaks for first
OL,4,Ctime about loss of his son
OL,6,FThe coroner's court heard the former
OL,7,Fboxer, known to fans as "The Hitman",
OL,8,Fwas in good spirits and, despite past
OL,9,Ftroubles with alcohol and drugs, had
OL,10,Fbeen the best "in years".
OL,12,FA Las Vegas themed tribute night is
OL,13,Fset to take place in Manchester in
OL,14,FJune called 'Evening4Ricky', to
OL,15,Fremember and celebrate his life.
OL,17,FRay Hatton said there are moments when
OL,18,Fthere is a "black cloud".
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
