OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778702756
OL,3,CRicky Hatton's dad speaks for first
OL,4,Ctime about loss of his son
OL,6,FHe said: "You never expect to lose
OL,7,Fyour children...so it makes it doubly
OL,8,Fhard.
OL,10,F"People say 'you have good days and
OL,11,Fbad days', you don't, you have good
OL,12,Fmoments and bad moments."
OL,14,F"But we couldn't have imagined how
OL,15,Fmuch people have thought about him.
OL,16,FThe pride that people have shown in
OL,17,Fknowing him... it's overwhelming at
OL,18,Ftimes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
